thread.title: Ray & Margaret
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Ray & Margaret

author: Ray & Margaret
title: Ray & Margaret
text: We had Jon, Mark and Laura assisting my wife and I with the sale of our Ascot vale property. They were attentive, responsive and on auction day negotiated between two parties immediately after our house was passed in. We were absolutely thrilled with the outcome. It was a very professional team and they facilitated an excellent sale price. We would have absolutely no hesitation in recommending Nelson Alexander to anyone.
